<p class="intro"><h2 style="margin-bottom: -20px;">CONTACT INFORMATION</h2>
</p>  
<div style="clear: both"></div>
<div class="row"><div class="col-60 col-sm-30 col-md-30"><div style="margin-bottom: -5px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 50px;"><img alt="Exhibitor PR Contact" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/exhibitor-pr-contact_505x285.jpg" />
<h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">List Your PR Contact Information</h3>
</div>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;">Include your company&rsquo;s PR contact within your CES 2018 directory listing, which is shared with registered CES media.</p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;">PR contacts also receive the <em>Exhibitor PR News </em>e-newsletter to stay on top of all PR programs and opportunities, important deadlines, and breaking show news.</p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><strong><a href="http://ces18.mapyourshow.com/7_0/search.cfm" target="_blank">Add or update your company&rsquo;s PR contact information.</a>&nbsp;&gt;</strong></p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><em>For log-in assistance, contact Map Your Show at 1-888-527-8823.&nbsp;</em></p>
</div><div class="col-60 col-sm-30 col-md-30"><div style="margin-bottom: -5px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 50px;"><a href="https://ces18.exh.mapyourshow.com/6_0/reports/customreport.cfm?ReportID=631" target="_blank"><img alt="See a list of registered media" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/registered-media_505x285.jpg" /></a>

<h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">See a List of Registered Media</h3>
</div>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><strong>Available Dec. 1, 2018</strong><br />
Pull targeted media lists for your news releases and media event pitches. The lists will be updated daily, and you can filter by product category.&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;">If you are hosting an official news conference at CES, the media list will be emailed to you one month in advance.&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><em>NOTE: Media choose whether to list a phone number or email. If none is listed, CES cannot release that information.</em></p>
</div><div class="clearfix visible-sm-block"></div><div class="clearfix visible-md-block visible-lg-block"></div></div><div style="clear: both;">&nbsp;</div>
<hr />
<h2 style="margin-bottom: -20px;"><br />
VIDEO OPPORTUNITIES</h2>

<div style="clear: both;">&nbsp;</div>
<div class="row"><div class="col-60 col-sm-30 col-md-30"><div style="margin-bottom: -5px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 50px;"><img alt="Press Pitch Video" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/pitch-video_505x285.JPG" />
<h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Submit a Pitch Video</h3>
</div>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;">Show the more than 7,000 media expected to attend CES what you&#39;re bringing to the show floor and why they should visit your booth with a pitch video, which will be posted on the CES website and YouTube.&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><strong><a href="/Exhibitor/Opportunities/Media-and-PR-Opportunities/Media-Outreach-Opportunities/Media-Pitch-Video-Form.aspx">Submit your pitch video.</a>&nbsp;&gt;</strong></p>
</div><div class="col-60 col-sm-30 col-md-30"><div style="margin-bottom: -5px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 50px;"><a href="/Exhibitor/Opportunities/Media-and-PR-Opportunities/Media-Outreach-Opportunities/CESTV-Coverage-Consideration-Form.aspx"><img alt="On-Site Video Coverage" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/on-site-video-coverage_505x285.jpg" /></a>
<h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Be in On-Site Video Coverage&nbsp;</h3>
</div>
<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><strong>Deadline: Dec. 15, 2017</strong><br />
Be part of <a href="/News/CES-TV?tag=CESTV">CESTV videos</a> that highlight hot products and new technologies on the CES show floor.&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><strong><a href="/Exhibitor/Media-and-PR-Opportunities/Media-Outreach-Opportunities/CESTV-Coverage-Consideration-Form.aspx">Apply for on-site CESTV coverage.</a>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;</strong></p>
<div></div>
</div><div class="clearfix visible-sm-block"></div><div class="clearfix visible-md-block visible-lg-block"></div></div><div style="clear: both;">&nbsp;</div>

<hr />
<h2 style="margin-bottom: -20px;"><br />
YEAR-ROUND OPPORTUNITIES</h2>

<div style="clear: both;">&nbsp;</div>
<div class="row"><div class="col-60 col-sm-30 col-md-30"><div style="margin-bottom: -5px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 50px;"><a href="mailto:prcontacts@ce.org?subject=2018%2520CES%2520Media%2520Tours%2520Inquiry"><img alt="Media Tour" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/media-tour_505x285.jpg" /></a><h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">CES Media Tours</h3>
</div>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;">Leading up to CES, help promote the excitement and buzz around the show by visting media in select cities. Learn how to be involved in media tours and have direct contact with media in your area.</p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><strong><a href="mailto:prcontacts@ce.org?subject=2018%2520CES%2520Media%2520Tours%2520Inquiry">Contact us.</a> &gt;</strong></p>
</div><div class="col-60 col-sm-30 col-md-30"><div style="margin-bottom: -5px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 50px;"><a href="/Exhibitor/Opportunities/Media-and-PR-Opportunities/Media-Outreach-Opportunities/CEA-s-Communications-Committee-Form.aspx"><img alt="CTA's Communications Committee" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/communications-committee_505x285.jpg" /></a><h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Join CTA&#39;s Communications Committee</h3>
</div>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;">Be part of the <a href="https://www.cta.tech/Membership/Divisions-Councils/Communications-Committee.aspx" target="_blank">Consumer Technology Association (CTA)&trade; Communications Committee</a>, which&nbsp;guides the design and implementation of &nbsp;public relations, media outreach, public affairs, consumer education, promotional campaigns, and related activities that suppor the consumer technology industry.&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><strong><a href="/Exhibitor/Opportunities/Media-and-PR-Opportunities/Media-Outreach-Opportunities/CEA-s-Communications-Committee-Form.aspx">Contact us to learn more.</a> &gt;</strong></p>
